    "name": "Oaths of Light - Chapter I",
    "steam_appid": 1549990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/68e28a9af66ed8704ca35c3979f5ac2c.poster.avif?t=1741596249\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/68e28a9af66ed8704ca35c3979f5ac2c.webm?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/68e28a9af66ed8704ca35c3979f5ac2c.mp4?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>Oaths of Light</strong>》是一款受到现代和经典JRPG启发的冒险游戏，融合了实时与回合制战斗系统，拥有具有后果的选择机制，设定在一个充满丰富历史的奇幻世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>具有实时元素的引人入胜的回合制战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗系统的灵感来自日式角色扮演经典：带有实时元素的回合制战斗。在你的回合中，你有五秒的时间来移动、攻击、使用物品或施放技能。你还可以防御敌人的攻击，只要他们不是从后面来的，这使得管理你的位置变得很重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/9c4a54c97b64aec81ed49ec6ab27f3b3.poster.avif?t=1741596249\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/9c4a54c97b64aec81ed49ec6ab27f3b3.webm?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/9c4a54c97b64aec81ed49ec6ab27f3b3.mp4?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>使用固定摄像头系统探索丰富多彩的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陪伴伊甸（Eden）踏入《光之誓言》的神秘魔法世界，她将踏上前往首都的旅程，参加光之誓言的仪式。在这次旅程的前后，将发生许多事件，这些事件将永远改变她的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/37ae2010c8ee75743909c691fd0be946.poster.avif?t=1741596249\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/37ae2010c8ee75743909c691fd0be946.webm?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/37ae2010c8ee75743909c691fd0be946.mp4?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>做出你的选择，并面对随之而来的后果。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在整个旅程中，你将面临一些需要做出决定的时刻，这些决定将直接影响故事的发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/c636cd8266e031e980d150f752bf5f23.poster.avif?t=1741596249\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/c636cd8266e031e980d150f752bf5f23.webm?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/c636cd8266e031e980d150f752bf5f23.mp4?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/37148cde9afd2c76f46ef3c122b7264b.webp?t=1741596249\" width=619 height=54 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/55a913fd5a41fdc0e74d5bbc3dc82d70.avif?t=1741596249\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的故事发生在梅德兰（Meadran）。这是一个因一场不久前的战争而仍然脆弱的世界。这场战争发生在梅德兰王国与森林之民——埃尔梅安人（Elmeians）之间。战争的核心原因是魔法。事实上，人们发现了一种将魔法用作能源的新用途。由于担心这种力量被滥用带来的后果，一场军备竞赛随之展开，最终导致战争爆发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的故事发生在战争结束十一年后。伤痕仍然鲜明，而胜利者梅德兰王国已经为魔法的使用制定了严格的规则和控制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切始于莱姆伯村（Reimber），这是我们的女主角伊甸（Eden）平静的家乡。一场令人不安且反复出现的梦境，村里有人离奇失踪，一位神秘的陌生人，以及一场意料之外的前往王国首都的旅程。这便是伊甸冒险的开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/f9858ce04c5ab6b69340166461e5f2f0.poster.avif?t=1741596249\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/f9858ce04c5ab6b69340166461e5f2f0.webm?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/f9858ce04c5ab6b69340166461e5f2f0.mp4?t=1741596249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
